Package: mrpbounds
Type: Package
Title: Bounds for Multilevel Regression and Poststratification (MRP) Estimates
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Moritz", "Marbach", role = c("aut", "cre"), email="m.marbach@ucl.ac.uk", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7101-2821")))
Description: Computes sharp bounds on multilevel regression and poststratification
    (MRP) estimates when the joint distribution of poststratification variables is
    only partially known. Given marginal or joint probability tables, the package
    uses linear programming to find the minimum and maximum possible values of MRP
    quantities, cell probabilities, and mean squared error.
